'''42街-港務局客運總站'''是一個位於[[IND第八大道線|IND第八大道線]]的快車[[地鐵站|地鐵站]]，部份位於[[紐新港務局客運總站|紐新港務局客運總站]]地下。設有一個月台層，兩個不對稱的[[島式月台|島式月台]]和一個長夾層。過去亦曾另外設有下層一個[[側式月台|側式月台]]。1932年9月10日上層啟用<ref name=Chambers/><ref name="Opening">{{cite news|last1=Crowell|first1=Paul|title=Gay Midnight Crowd Rides First Trains In The New Subway: Throngs at Station an Hour Before Time, Rush Turnstiles When Chains are Dropped|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9507E2D61231E633A25753C1A96F9C946394D6CF|accessdate=8 November 2015|publisher=紐約市報|date=September 10, 1932|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810014338/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9507E2D61231E633A25753C1A96F9C946394D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>而下層於1952年8月25日啟用<ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwrLvl-1952 />。

=== 月台層 ===
車站的月台層設有兩個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和四條軌道，北行月台由42街延至44街；南行月台由40街延至42街。車站的夾層由40街延至44街，並於41街設有一條長通道連接複合的其他部分<ref name=MTA-TimesSquare-2015>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: Pennsylvania Station/Times Square|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/mn/M08_PennStation_2015.pdf|website=[[大都會運輸署|mta.info]]|publisher=[[大都會運輸署|大都會運輸署]]|accessdate=December 11, 2015|date=2015|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914173833/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/mn/M08_PennStation_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nycsubway.org">{{cite web | url = http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/Station:_42nd_Street-Port_Authority_Bus_Terminal_%288th_Avenue%29 | title = Station: 42nd Street-Port Authority Bus Terminal (8th Avenue) | accessdate = April 6, 2013 | archive-date = 2015-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151009102638/http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/Station:_42nd_Street-Port_Authority_Bus_Terminal_(8th_Avenue) | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 舊下層 ===
除了現時使用中的樓層外，過去南行一側曾經設有一個下側月台（一條軌道位於下城普通軌道的下面，另外一個側式月台位於島式月台的下面）。下層與上層的月台於1920年代末至1930年代初同時興建，但直至1952年8月前仍為未完成的空殻。1952年8月啟用提供繁忙時段E線列車服務<ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwrLvl-1952>{{cite web|title=New IND Platform Will Open Monday|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9F06E0D8123AE23BBC4B51DFBE668389649EDE|website=[[紐約時報|nytimes.com]]|publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|accessdate=June 30, 2015|date=August 23, 1952}}</ref><ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwr-Expedite-1952 />。多數情況下，下層月台只是間中作特殊服務，包括於1958年開始的夏季「Rockaway Special」列車往[[海灘98街車站_(IND洛克威線)|海灘98街車站]]方便前往{{link-en|洛克威遊樂場|Rockaways' Playland}}，另外1959－1981年間設有特殊車費列車前往[[水道賽車場車站_(IND洛克威線)|水道賽車場車站]]，與1970年3月23日開始於尖峰時段營運的E線列車<ref name="NYT2008">{{cite news |first=Alex |last=Mindlin |title=No Whoosh, No ‘All Aboard’ |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/20/nyregion/thecity/20port.html |work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date=April 20, 2008 |accessdate=July 10, 2009 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223212535/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/20/nyregion/thecity/20port.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SASblog2008">{{cite web | url = http://secondavenuesagas.com/2008/04/21/with-the-7-on-the-way-a-swan-song-for-a-times-square-platform/ | title = With the 7 on the way, a swan song for a Times Square platform | last = Kabak | first = Benjamin | date = April 21, 2008 | accessdate = April 6, 2013 | archive-date = 2020-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201027171951/http://secondavenuesagas.com/2008/04/21/with-the-7-on-the-way-a-swan-song-for-a-times-square-platform/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/42st.html |title=Abandoned Stations: 42 St Lower Level |first=Joseph |last=Brennan |year=2002 |accessdate=May 4, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111225134/http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/42st.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Non-Stop Trips, Reserved Seats On Special Here: Deluxe Subway Express Ride Also Features Music; $1.55 Round-Trip Fare From 42nd Street To Playland Station Provides Admission And Rides|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252021%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2520%25201958%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2520%25201958%2520-%25200286.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F652bb2fd7e9ec6c4f0e39d15f1b10cf5#page=1|accessdate=17 August 2016|work=[[Wave_of_Long_Island|Wave of Long Island]]|agency=[[Fultonhistory.com|Fultonhistory.com]]|date=July 3, 1958|page=1|archive-date=2022-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220619171813/https://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspapers%252021%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2520%25201958%2FRockaway%2520Beach%2520NY%2520%2520Wave%2520Of%2520Long%2520Island%2520%25201958%2520-%25200286.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F652bb2fd7e9ec6c4f0e39d15f1b10cf5#page=1}}</ref>。

下層設有兩條高速扶手電梯前往夾層和三條樓梯往上層月台<ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwrLvl-1952/><ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwr-Expedite-1952>{{cite web|last1=Ingraham|first1=Joseph C.|title=New IND Platform at 8th and 42d To Expedite Service From Queens|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9805E1D91F3DE53ABC4851DFB0668389649EDE|website=[[紐約時報|nytimes.com]]|publisher=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|accessdate=30 June 2015|date=June 20, 1952}}</ref><ref name=NYT2008 />。

興建下層月台有不同的解釋。月台只能透過由[[皇后區|皇后區]]出發經[[IND皇后林蔭路線|IND皇后林蔭路線]]和53街（現時的E線列車）進出。部分評論者指出這容許往曼哈頓的E線列車由皇后區開出並長時間停留在42街而不影響由中央公園西開出的列車<ref name="SASblog2008" />，而報告指出月台的用途為容許E線列車上下客而不需等待上層月台兩條軌道清空<ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwrLvl-1952 /><ref name=NYTimes-42PABTLwr-Expedite-1952 />。其他人亦指下層月台的興建為阻止[[IRT法拉盛線|IRT法拉盛線]]西延。IND的下層月台位於IRT法拉盛線月台的尾端軌道<ref name="nycsubway.org" /><ref name="SASblog2008" /><ref name="flickr2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/benyankee/11468884304/in/set-72157638861830194/|title=7 Line Extension 081|work=Flickr|access-date=2016-12-23|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208051505/https://www.flickr.com/photos/benyankee/11468884304/in/set-72157638861830194/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一些製片者使用下層月台進行拍攝，包括《[[人鬼情未了|人鬼情未了]]》（1990年）<ref name="NYT2008" /><ref name="SASblog2008" />。
	
2000年代末，[[大都會運輸署|大都會運輸署]]開始興建[[紐約地鐵7號線延伸段|IRT法拉盛線的延伸段]]往[[34街-哈德遜調車場車站_(IRT法拉盛線)|34街車站]]，並需要拆除IND第八大道線下層月台<ref name="SASblog2008" />。下層月台已經於2010年1月拆除<ref>{{cite news |title=Abandoned No More: 2nd Life Drilled into Old 7 Subway Platform |first=Pete |last=Donohue |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2009/06/20/2009-06-20_abandoned_no_more_2nd_life_drilled_into_old_7_subway_platform.html |newspaper=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|New York Daily News]] |date=June 20, 2009 |accessdate=January 30, 2010 |archive-date=2009-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090623061323/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/2009/06/20/2009-06-20_abandoned_no_more_2nd_life_drilled_into_old_7_subway_platform.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一名受邀參觀法拉盛線延伸段工場進度的交通博客於2012年2月回報指下層月台已由法拉盛線延伸段切開<ref name="SASblog2012">{{cite web | url = http://secondavenuesagas.com/2012/02/12/photos-inside-the-7-line-extension/ | title = Photos: Inside the 7 line extension | last = Kabak | first = Benjamin | date = February 12, 2012 | accessdate = April 6, 2013 | archive-date = 2014-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006115657/http://secondavenuesagas.com/2012/02/12/photos-inside-the-7-line-extension/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。隧道下斜通過舊下層月台的所在地<ref name="flickr2013"/>。
