== 事件 ==
2017年12月11日早高峰时段，连接IND第八大道线车站和站台其他地方的人行道有[[管道炸弹|管道炸弹]]爆炸，造成4人受伤<ref>{{cite web | last=Griggs | first=Troy | last2=Lai | first2=K.K. Rebecca | last3=Wallace | first3=Tim | title=Where the Port Authority Subway Explosion Happened | website=The New York Times | date=2017-12-11 | url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/12/11/nyregion/port-authority-subway-explosion-maps.html | access-date=2017-12-12 | archive-date=2017-12-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211174135/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/12/11/nyregion/port-authority-subway-explosion-maps.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。嫌犯是27岁的孟加拉移民阿卡耶德·乌拉赫（Akayed Ullah）被怀疑是恐怖份子，他受伤后被送往医院<ref>{{cite news|last1=Celona|first1=Larry|title=Suspected bomber in custody after explosion at Port Authority|url=https://nypost.com/2017/12/11/explosion-reported-at-port-authority-bus-terminal/|accessdate=2017-12-11|publisher=New York Post|date=2017-12-11|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211132501/https://nypost.com/2017/12/11/explosion-reported-at-port-authority-bus-terminal/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Rashbaum|first1=William|title=Pipe Bomb Explodes in New York Subway Walkway|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/11/nyregion/explosion-times-square.html|accessdate=2017-12-11|publisher=New York Times|date=2017-12-11|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211133829/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/12/11/nyregion/explosion-times-square.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/12/11/us/manhattan-new-york-explosion-latest/index.html|title=New York City explosion: Live updates|first=Meg|last=Wagner|first2=Amanda|last2=Wills|date=2017-12-11|work=CNN|access-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328124630/https://www.cnn.com/2017/12/11/us/manhattan-new-york-explosion-latest/index.html|archive-date=2020-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

